        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span>&nbsp;Interact</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Your features become striking and your voice becomes musical and commanding, though facts and figures become hazy for you and emotion clouds your ability to reason.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit&nbsp;</strong>You gain a +2 item bonus to Deception, Diplomacy, Intimidation and Performance checks. Your critical failures with any of these skills become failures instead.</p>\n<p><strong>Drawback</strong>&nbsp;You take a -2 item penalty to Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, and Society checks. Choose one skill in which you are trained; for the duration, you become untrained in that skill. All your failures to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} become critical failures.</p>\n<p><strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;10 minutes.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.v5Ht1V4MZvRKRBjL]{Effect: Silvertongue Mutagen (Moderate)}</p>",
